[Warm Boudoir]

125
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:26,710
Is Ruofei there?

126
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:28,310
I heard that an assassin injured Ruofei yesterday.

127
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,110
How is she?

128
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,550
Ruofei is in the room.

129
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:32,270
But the Young Lord is also there.

130
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,730
I think it's better not to disturb them, sir.

131
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:38,030
The Young Lord is in Ruofei's room?

132
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:38,590
Yes.

133
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:41,200
Well, not exactly.

134
00:07:41,990 --> 00:07:43,190
Su Ruofei's room

135
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,590
is the Young Lord's room.

136
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,200
Wait, did you mean...

137
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:52,390
Ruofei and the Young Lord are living in the same room?

138
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:54,060
That's right.

139
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,390
[Warm Boudoir]

140
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,070
Mr. Jin.
[Warm Boudoir]

141
