148
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:37,990
Ruofei.

149
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:40,880
Shangyu.

150
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,450
Why are you here?

151
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:53,260
What are you two doing?

152
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:56,230
Mr. Jin, you've intruded into my bedchamber without permission.

153
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,040
May I ask the reason for your visit?

154
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,300
I'm here to see Ruofei.

155
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:01,670
I heard you were injured by an assassin.

156
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:03,470
I came specially to check on you.

157
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:06,080
I didn't know you two were living together.

158
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,590
Shangyu.

159
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:12,710
You've misunderstood.

160
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:14,470
I sleep in this big bed.

161
00:09:14,470 --> 00:09:16,510
The Young Lord sleeps in that small bed over there.

162
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,880
There's a screen between us.

163
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,610
See?

164
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,850
You sleep in the big bed.

165
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:26,830
The Young Lord sleeps in the small bed.

166
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:27,470
What?

167
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:30,550
I pamper my entertainer by letting her sleep in the big bed.

168
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:32,750
Do you have a problem with that, Mr. Jin?

169
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:35,070
No.

170
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:40,100
Mr. Jin, you've never been one to fuss over minor details,

171
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,110
but barging into my bedchamber

172
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,270
is extremely disrespectful.

173
00:09:44,810 --> 00:09:45,670
I'm afraid I won't be able to

174
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:47,600
continue to host you in my mansion.

175
00:09:48,230 --> 00:09:49,560
It's my fault this time.

176
00:09:50,110 --> 00:09:52,110
