191
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:43,460
Let's talk this through calmly.

192
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:45,600
It's not a big deal.

193
00:10:46,070 --> 00:10:47,000
Shangyu.

194
00:10:47,350 --> 00:10:50,630
There's nothing between the Young Lord and me.

195
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:53,230
He was just helping me apply medicine here.

196
00:10:54,340 --> 00:10:55,160
Young Lord.

197
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:57,510
Shangyu is my best friend.

198
00:10:57,590 --> 00:10:59,510
He might've been overly concerned about me,

199
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:01,240
