200
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:03,240
This doesn't concern you.

201
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:04,660
Go back and lie down.

202
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,270
Xiaoqi.

203
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,720
