Mr. Jin, please.

207
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:23,930
Ruofei.

208
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:25,070
Take good rest.

209
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,350
I'll come to see you another day.

210
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,190
I'll see him off.

211
00:11:37,310 --> 00:11:37,950
Come back.

212
