233
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,960
What exquisite konghou skills!

234
00:12:58,700 --> 00:12:59,510
This trip was worth it.

235
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,640
Really impressive.

236
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:20,510
Ms. Su

237
00:13:20,610 --> 00:13:22,990
