I didn't dare to disturb you.

276
00:15:06,050 --> 00:15:08,430
I even waited for you at the door for a while.

277
00:15:08,430 --> 00:15:09,490
Come on. Come here.

278
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:10,810
Take a look at this.

279
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:17,550
I found the best embroidery workshop in Symphony City

280
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:18,740
and had a set of embroidered clothes made for you.

281
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:19,910
See if you like it.

282
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:21,070
Come on. Have a seat.

283
00:15:24,070 --> 00:15:26,080
Mayor, there's no need for such extravagance.

284
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,400
I've told you before

285
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,970
I don't lack anything here.

286
00:15:29,350 --> 00:15:32,200
Besides, these embroidered clothes are clearly costly.

287
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,700
I can't accept such a gift.

288
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,390
In a few days, the Symphony Workshop

289
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:38,460
will hold the Flowing Stream Musical Gathering.

290
00:15:38,460 --> 00:15:40,030
You'll definitely need this.

291
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:40,830
Keep it.

292
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:42,700
Oh, right.

293
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:45,060
I also had a Cloud City–style carriage

294
00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:46,150
made for you.

295
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,150
It will be ready in a while.

296
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,340
I'll have it delivered to you directly.

297
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:49,990
By the way,

298
00:15:50,470 --> 00:15:52,670
are you comfortable in this residence?

299
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,350
I can buy another house for you

300
00:15:55,350 --> 00:15:56,670
near the Symphony Workshop.

301
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:58,750
Mayor, please don't worry.

302
00:15:58,770 --> 00:16:01,950
I'm quite comfortable living here in the Symphony Workshop.

303
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:03,870
Well then, you can't refuse the carriage.

304
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:05,070
It will be ready soon.

305
00:16:05,910 --> 00:16:08,750
Then, thank you, Mayor.

306
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:12,040
I will certainly perform well

307
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,270
and showcase the elegance

308
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:15,030
of our Cloud City musicians to everyone.

309
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,180
Of course.

310
00:16:16,430 --> 00:16:17,960
When you stand there,

311
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:20,530
you'll definitely be the most outstanding.

312
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:25,220
Oh, Shanshan,

313
00:16:25,470 --> 00:16:28,870
do you know what the Flowing Stream Musical Gathering is for?

314
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:30,670
I heard it was a grand music event

315
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:32,070
held by Madam Yaoshan

316
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:34,130
after she became the music minister.

317
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:35,490
It's more than that.

318
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:37,690
I've inquired about it in detail.

319
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:40,170
In previous years, many musicians

320
00:16:40,220 --> 00:16:43,750
start a relationship through music pairing at this gathering.

321
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:46,110
So, I came to ask you

322
00:16:46,350 --> 00:16:47,950
what piece you'll play by then.

323
00:16:47,950 --> 00:16:49,950
I'll play a piece to respond to yours.

324
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:52,150
Mayor, your hands are meant for battling enemies,

325
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:54,000
not for playing musical instruments.

326
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,430
Why lower yourself to this?

327
00:16:55,430 --> 00:16:56,990
No, no, it's not lowering myself.

328
00:16:56,990 --> 00:16:58,320
Don't worry, Shanshan.

329
00:16:58,350 --> 00:16:59,710
I've already found some teachers.

330
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:01,240
I will practice diligently

331
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,470
and won't embarrass you in front of everyone.

332
00:17:03,470 --> 00:17:04,590
No, Mayor.

333
00:17:04,630 --> 00:17:05,150
-I...
-Alright.

334
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:06,750
I won't disturb your practice anymore.

335
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,310
I should go back and practice as well.

336
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,670
You don't need to see me out.

337
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:13,130
Let's see each other at the Flowing Stream Musical Gathering.

338
00:17:13,190 --> 00:17:13,990
Don't see me out. Don't.

339
00:17:13,990 --> 00:17:15,520
-Keep practicing.
-Mayor.

340
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:19,960
I'm leaving.

341
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:27,560
I wonder if the Young Lord will attend the gathering.

342
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:43,910
Does he only feel gratitude towards that jasper girl

343
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,960
and nothing else?

344
00:17:47,850 --> 00:17:49,050
No matter what,

345
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:51,140
that jasper girl holds a special place

346
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:52,370
in his heart.

347
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:55,070
At this gathering,

348
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:57,270
I must match my music with his.

349
00:17:57,730 --> 00:17:59,330
Only then can we get closer.

350
00:18:02,580 --> 00:18:06,220
[Young Lord's Mansion]

351
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:09,100
Two heavy, one light.

352
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,400
Two light.

353
00:18:12,190 --> 00:18:12,950
Ruofei.

354
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,790
Shangyu.

355
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,090
Shangyu.

356
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:24,230
Why are you sneaking around secretly?

357
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:25,440
The Young Lord ordered

358
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,710
to prevent me from seeing you,

359
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:27,950
so I had to sneak in by climbing over the wall.

360
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:29,170
Prevent you from seeing me?

361
00:18:29,170 --> 00:18:29,810
Why?

362
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,160
Never mind. Let's not talk about that.

363
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:33,670
Ruofei,

364
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:35,250
I recently looked at a house.

365
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:37,080
The scenery is beautiful, and the environment is elegant.

366
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:38,170
I've bought it.

367
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:39,810
Will you leave with me?

368
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:42,790
Leave with you?

369
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:48,070
Or, if you don't want to stay in Symphony City,

370
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,870
I can take you back to Cloud City.

371
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:51,480
Or, wherever you want to go,

372
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:52,640
I can take you there.

373
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,310
Thank you, Shangyu.

374
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:59,790
But I can't leave with you.

375
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,860
W-why not?

376
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:04,410
Do you really want to be his entertainer?

377
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:06,600
I don't just want to be an entertainer.

378
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,580
I am...

379
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:10,510
I can't tell him about the ear thing.

380
00:19:11,910 --> 00:19:14,600
Anyway, I have my reasons for staying.

381
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,040
Oh, and the Young Lord promised me,

382
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:19,550
as long as I perform well as his entertainer,

383
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:21,340
he will help me restore my music status

384
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:22,610
and enter the Symphony Workshop.

385
00:19:22,610 --> 00:19:23,750
Symphony Workshop?

386
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:26,070
I remember you always hated

387
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:27,310
those official workshops.

388
00:19:27,310 --> 00:19:30,420
But the Symphony Workshop is not an ordinary official workshop.

389
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:33,110
Not only do I want to enter the Symphony Workshop,

390
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:35,350
but I also want to become the music minister.

391
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:36,480
The music minister?

392
00:19:36,870 --> 00:19:37,510
Why?

393
00:19:38,670 --> 00:19:41,000
Because once I become the music minister,

394
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,150
I can change

395
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:44,070
those annoying systems.

396
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:46,230
Talented musicians

397
00:19:46,230 --> 00:19:47,630
like Monkey, Eleven, and Biao

398
00:19:47,630 --> 00:19:49,150
won't be discriminated against anymore.

399
00:19:49,150 --> 00:19:50,820
They will be respected instead.

400
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:52,350
Moreover, the private workshops

401
00:19:52,350 --> 00:19:54,790
can be on equal footing with official workshops.

402
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:56,350
I just hope those who think they're above others

403
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:58,150
and are so full of themselves can realize

404
00:19:58,150 --> 00:20:00,480
that music is not just about lofty ideals.

405
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:03,110
It should be more about bringing joy to people.

406
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:07,730
Since you have such ambitions,

407
00:20:07,730 --> 00:20:08,950
I'll wait for you at the Symphony Workshop.

408
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:09,550
Alright.

409
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:11,110
But are you sure

410
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:12,670
the Young Lord will keep his promise?

411
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:13,780
Don't worry.

412
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:15,850
The Young Lord made a promise to me.

413
00:20:16,020 --> 00:20:18,420
Besides, he still needs something from me.

414
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:20,540
Okay.

415
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:24,060
Someone's coming. I have to go now.

416
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,120
-Take care.
-Okay.

417
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,840
What are you doing here?

418
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:37,990
I was just feeling a bit tired from practicing,

419
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:39,550
so I'm taking a break here.

420
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:41,590
What instructions do you have, Young Lord?

421
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:43,190
I've thought of a new method.

422
00:20:43,630 --> 00:20:44,790
It can also test

423
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:48,120
the results of your recent practice with the bell language.

424
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:57,370
[Chengxin Pavilion]

425
00:20:57,370 --> 00:20:58,980
I called you here today
[Chengxin Pavilion]

426
00:20:58,980 --> 00:20:59,110
[Chengxin Pavilion]

427
00:20:59,110 --> 00:21:00,960
to play a little game.
[Chengxin Pavilion]

428
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:01,030
[Chengxin Pavilion]

429
00:21:01,390 --> 00:21:03,270
Later, I will blindfold myself

430
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:05,260
and shoot these arrows at you.

431
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:06,590
Of course,

432
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:08,330
whoever can hold out till the end

433
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:10,450
will be rewarded handsomely.

434
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,670
This little devil is so full of tricks.

435
00:21:12,670 --> 00:21:15,350
He's testing my bell language with such an elaborate setup.

436
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:18,110
All are dolled up, with singing and dancing.

437
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:19,930
Isn't he afraid of being overwhelmed by the fragrance?

438
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:20,660
How about it?

439
00:21:20,690 --> 00:21:21,710
Are you ready?

440
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,110
We're ready.

441
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:24,580
Then, let's begin.

442
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,410
Let's go over there, quickly.

443
00:21:38,730 --> 00:21:39,230
[Chengxin Pavilion]

444
00:21:53,710 --> 00:21:54,710
Southeast.

445
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:03,760
Northeast to the East.

446
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:12,630
West.

447
00:22:13,150 --> 00:22:13,960
[Chengxin Pavilion]

448
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:27,590
[Chengxin Pavilion]

449
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:28,920
Northwest to the North.
[Chengxin Pavilion]

450
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,660
[Chengxin Pavilion]

451
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:35,880
East.

452
00:22:50,990 --> 00:22:51,690
North.

453
00:23:09,310 --> 00:23:10,440
Alright, everyone,

454
00:23:10,540 --> 00:23:11,990
go inside to collect your gold leaves.

455
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:12,150
Thank you, Young Lord.

456
00:23:12,150 --> 00:23:13,280
[Chengxin Pavilion]
Thank you, Young Lord.

457
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:15,400
[Chengxin Pavilion]

458
00:23:17,990 --> 00:23:19,750
Tell me, why did you shoot at me?

459
00:23:19,780 --> 00:23:21,840
Couldn't you hear the bell language…

460
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,830
Your voice was so loud.

461
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,830
Were you trying to reveal my secret?

462
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,110
Then, tell me.

463
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,940
Why didn't you follow the bell language instructions I gave you?

464
00:23:30,940 --> 00:23:32,690
If I really let you win the grand prize,

465
00:23:32,690 --> 00:23:34,570
wouldn't you ask for the moon?

466
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:37,910
But don't worry,

467
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:40,740
I've prepared some extra gold leaves for you.

468
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:42,890
Consider it a bonus reward.

469
00:23:45,630 --> 00:23:46,670
I didn't expect it, either.

470
00:23:46,670 --> 00:23:48,790
The Young Lord's arrow was pointing at me.

471
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:50,150
I thought I was surely going to lose.

472
00:23:50,150 --> 00:23:51,710
Haven't you figured it out yet?

473
00:23:51,710 --> 00:23:52,830
The game today

474
00:23:52,830 --> 00:23:55,310
was designed by the Young Lord to cheer up Su Ruofei.

475
00:23:55,310 --> 00:23:56,640
What do you mean by that?

476
00:23:56,710 --> 00:23:58,440
You think you got the top prize,

477
00:23:58,550 --> 00:23:59,670
but the Young Lord must have

478
00:23:59,670 --> 00:24:01,700
given Su Ruofei even more in private.

479
00:24:01,700 --> 00:24:03,570
This is what they call "spending a fortune

480
00:24:03,570 --> 00:24:05,050
to make a beauty smile."

481
00:24:05,710 --> 00:24:06,950
We're all entertainers,

482
00:24:06,950 --> 00:24:09,350
but the Young Lord treats her differently.

483
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:11,820
It's clear that she's an entertainer on the surface,

484
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:14,220
but in reality, she's a favored concubine.

485
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:20,060
One, two, three, four, five, six.

486
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:21,580
Six gold leaves.

487
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,100
Do you think it's too little?

488
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:25,790
At least my efforts weren't in vain.

489
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:27,310
My hands are sore.

490
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:28,870
Young Lord.

491
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:30,050
Ms. Su has arrived.

492
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:30,900
Sister.

493
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:31,790
Ruoshan is here.

494
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:33,120
Greetings, Young Lord.

495
00:24:33,670 --> 00:24:34,300
Sister.

496
00:24:36,090 --> 00:24:37,870
I've missed you so much.

497
00:24:37,950 --> 00:24:39,150
I've missed you, too.

498
00:24:39,550 --> 00:24:40,880
Come, sit down quickly.

499
00:24:41,050 --> 00:24:42,000
Come, sit.

500
00:24:45,430 --> 00:24:46,850
You also want to sit?

501
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:48,230
Go stand over there.

502
00:24:55,050 --> 00:24:56,310
It's been days since I've seen Fei.

503
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:58,110
I've been missing her very much.

504
00:24:58,110 --> 00:25:00,310
Today, I can finally put my mind at ease.

505
00:25:00,810 --> 00:25:04,120
Thank you, Young Lord, for taking such good care of my sister

506
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:05,720
and being so tolerant of her.

507
00:25:05,730 --> 00:25:07,140
Ruoshan, you're being too polite.

508
00:25:07,140 --> 00:25:08,270
Come, have some tea.

509
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:12,050
Last time you came, I happened to have urgent matters,

510
00:25:12,050 --> 00:25:13,580
so I couldn't meet with you.

511
00:25:13,850 --> 00:25:16,470
I wonder if you've been comfortable staying at the Symphony Workshop lately.

512
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:18,790
If you need anything, remember to come to me.

513
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:20,030
I appreciate your concern, Young Lord.

514
00:25:20,030 --> 00:25:21,260
I'm doing well.

515
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:23,230
I've come unannounced today,

516
00:25:23,230 --> 00:25:24,760
not just to visit my sister,

517
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,200
but most importantly…

518
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:28,340
It's because the Flowing Stream Musical Gathering is approaching.

519
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:30,820
I hope you can grace us with your presence.

520
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:34,170
[Invitation of Flowing Stream Musical Gathering]

521
00:25:40,390 --> 00:25:41,850
[Invitation of Flowing Stream Musical Gathering]

522
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:44,360
The Flowing Stream Musical Gathering?

523
00:25:44,620 --> 00:25:45,550
What's that for?

524
00:25:45,970 --> 00:25:46,500
[Invitation of Flowing Stream Musical Gathering]

525
00:25:46,770 --> 00:25:47,830
Did I tell you to touch?

526
00:25:47,830 --> 00:25:50,230
If you touch again, go practice over there.

527
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:53,350
Fine.

528
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:58,190
[Invitation of Flowing Stream Musical Gathering]

529
00:26:01,670 --> 00:26:02,990
Since you're inviting me,

530
00:26:02,990 --> 00:26:04,920
I will certainly attend in person.

531
00:26:05,760 --> 00:26:07,020
Thank you, Young Lord.

532
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:10,910
Sister,

533
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,750
is the Symphony Workshop fun?

534
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:16,420
Those musicians must be really good, right?

535
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:17,680
Are they as good as you?

536
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:20,150
Fei,

537
00:26:20,340 --> 00:26:21,870
tell me the truth.

538
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:25,810
What exactly are you doing in the Young Lord's Mansion?

539
00:26:26,150 --> 00:26:27,910
Haven't I already told you?

540
00:26:27,940 --> 00:26:29,370
Sister, as you know,

541
00:26:29,410 --> 00:26:31,670
I'm just here to be a little entertainer.

542
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:33,110
But I've heard

543
00:26:33,710 --> 00:26:37,030
you're the Young Lord's favored concubine.

544
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:41,580
Who told you that?

545
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:43,070
Don't listen to such nonsense.

546
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,390
That little devil and I

547
00:26:44,390 --> 00:26:45,710
have absolutely no relationship.

548
00:26:45,710 --> 00:26:47,630
There's completely nothing between us.

549
00:26:47,630 --> 00:26:48,350
Fei,

550
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:50,470
as an entertainer in the Young Lord's Mansion,

551
00:26:50,470 --> 00:26:52,430
