00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:15,000
was none other than the current Madam Yaoshan.

828
00:39:15,250 --> 00:39:17,860
That gathering brought together many beautiful couples.

829
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:19,300
My husband and I

830
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,320
also met at that gathering.

831
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:24,200
I hope that under my witness,

832
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,810
everyone can find their perfect match

833
00:39:25,810 --> 00:39:27,740
and let music seal the affections.

834
00:39:32,700 --> 00:39:34,230
What did Minister Ling say?

835
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:37,120
Minister Ling said

836
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,370
that she and her husband

837
00:39:38,370 --> 00:39:40,370
met at this very musical gathering.

838
00:39:44,600 --> 00:39:47,360
It seems this is truly a matchmaking event.

839
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,130
Did you really not know?

840
00:39:51,790 --> 00:39:53,920
When you're conveying messages to me,

841
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:55,560
don't eat anything.

842
00:39:55,870 --> 00:39:58,270
You're chewing and talking at the same time.

843
00:39:58,270 --> 00:40:00,200
How am I supposed to read your lips?

844
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,910
Does no one speak to you

845
00:40:07,910 --> 00:40:08,990
while eating?

846
00:40:10,940 --> 00:40:13,150
Except for my parents and my uncle,

847
00:40:13,330 --> 00:40:15,740
no one dares to speak to me while eating.

848
00:40:16,470 --> 00:40:17,150
Oh, right.

849
00:40:17,250 --> 00:40:19,110
If someone starts playing later,

850
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:21,770
use the bell language to convey the message to me.

851
00:40:21,770 --> 00:40:22,610
Remember,

852
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:25,660
if you get it wrong, there will be consequences.

853
00:40:26,490 --> 00:40:28,020
Even if I play it wrong,

854
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,370
you wouldn't even know.

855
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,350
What did you say?

856
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,170
It has begun.

857
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:50,330
Not bad flute playing.

858
00:41:01,660 --> 00:41:03,230
Is Young Lord really just bringing Fei

859
00:41:03,230 --> 00:41:04,630
to broaden her horizons?

860
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:25,460
Ah, the Purple Bamboo Melody.

861
00:41:26,310 --> 00:41:27,630
Correct.

862
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:29,130
Good job.

863
00:41:29,170 --> 00:41:29,930
Continue.

864
00:41:42,430 --> 00:41:44,230
They really did end up together.

865
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:48,160
Don't forget our main task.

866
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:49,080
I remember.

867
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:09,780
What's wrong?

868
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:10,960
Are you tired?

869
00:42:12,270 --> 00:42:12,940
No.

870
00:42:15,350 --> 00:42:16,350
Give me your hand.

871
00:42:16,530 --> 00:42:17,920
I'm fine.

872
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:32,800
You have this medicine with you all the time?

873
00:42:33,410 --> 00:42:34,250
Let me do it myself.

874
00:42:34,250 --> 00:42:35,310
Don't move around.

875
00:42:40,790 --> 00:42:43,890
If it's an ordinary tune later,

876
00:42:44,110 --> 00:42:46,220
you don't need to mimic it for me again.

877
00:42:46,220 --> 00:42:47,980
When you're interested,

878
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,880
you can mimic it for me again.

879
00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:54,560
At least you have some conscience.

880
00:42:58,650 --> 00:43:00,660
Your skin is so delicate.

881
00:43:00,810 --> 00:43:02,420
How can you

882
00:43:02,450 --> 00:43:03,710
be my ears constantly?

883
00:43:04,030 --> 00:43:05,890
It seems you still lack practice.

884
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:07,750
Once you develop calluses,

885
00:43:07,750 --> 00:43:09,750
naturally, you won't hurt anymore.

886
00:43:18,230 --> 00:43:19,330
It's my sister!

887
00:43:26,760 --> 00:43:27,560
Young Lord.

888
00:43:28,030 --> 00:43:29,210
This song...

889
00:43:29,480 --> 00:43:31,410
I'm sure you haven't forgotten it.

890
00:43:32,670 --> 00:43:34,310
Isn't this the Green Flash Chant written by

891
00:43:34,310 --> 00:43:35,460
Madam Yaoshan?

892
00:43:36,180 --> 00:43:38,380
Sister is actually playing this piece.

893
00:43:39,710 --> 00:43:41,560
But if it were me,

894
00:43:41,590 --> 00:43:42,720
I would play it, too.

895
00:43:43,110 --> 00:43:44,710
This is my favorite piece.

896
00:43:46,160 --> 00:43:47,820
What song did you hear

897
00:43:48,070 --> 00:43:49,100
that made you so excited?

898
00:43:49,100 --> 00:43:51,700
It's the Green Flash Song, played by my sister.

899
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:54,760
Her skills are indeed exceptional.

900
00:44:17,220 --> 00:44:18,500
Let me play it for you.

901
00:44:25,630 --> 00:44:26,510
Is that the feeling

902
00:44:26,510 --> 00:44:28,190
Ruoshan wants to convey to me?

903
00:44:29,380 --> 00:44:30,620
The jasper girl.
